                <li><strong>iOS:</strong><span>&nbsp;</span>11.0+ (iPad only). Must have a compatible LMS integration.<span>&nbsp;</span><a href="http://respondus.com/can-an-ipad-be-used-with-lockdown-browser-instructions-for-faculty" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Details</a></li>
